FACLOCID: Theses buildings have a PARKNUM attribute in FMSS that does not match the PARKID in GIS (which was historically populated from FMSS)
The GIS has been updated to align with FMSS.  This documents the old and new ParkIDs.
In some cases the FMSS ParkID does not match the FMSS description
In some cases the PARKID is inconsistent (hyphen or not) in a set of buildings.
In some cases (street addresses) the Park ID in GIS was more descriptive/complete
Cleanup would be nice but it needs to start in FMSS.
